A mom in North Dakota was so upset by her 18-year-old daughter’s recent behavior that she sold the girl’s tickets to see Katy Perry in concert next month as punishment.

Cindy Bjerke of Fargo posted a short ad on the Fargo Moorhead Online Garage Sale Facebook page in order to discipline her daughter.

Bjerke didn’t name her daughter but described her in unflattering terms as a ‘spoiled brat’ who ‘doesn't deserve these tickets’.

